Terminals unused in grammar

    NEQ
    LE
    GE
    COMMA


Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: statement_list

    2 statement_list: statement
    3               | statement_list statement

    4 statement: declaration
    5          | assignment
    6          | if_statement
    7          | while_statement
    8          | print_statement
    9          | return_statement

   10 type: INT
   11     | FLOAT

   12 declaration: type IDENTIFIER SEMICOLON
   13            | type IDENTIFIER ASSIGN expression SEMICOLON

   14 assignment: IDENTIFIER ASSIGN expression SEMICOLON

   15 if_statement: IF LPAREN expression RPAREN LBRACE statement_list RBRACE
   16             | IF LPAREN expression RPAREN LBRACE statement_list RBRACE ELSE LBRACE statement_list RBRACE

   17 while_statement: WHILE LPAREN expression RPAREN LBRACE statement_list RBRACE

   18 print_statement: PRINT LPAREN expression RPAREN SEMICOLON

   19 return_statement: RETURN expression SEMICOLON

   20 expression: term
   21           | expression PLUS term
   22           | expression MINUS term
   23           | expression EQ term
   24           | expression LT term
   25           | expression GT term

   26 term: factor
   27     | term MULT factor
   28     | term DIV factor

   29 factor: INT_LITERAL
   30       | FLOAT_LITERAL
   31       | IDENTIFIER
   32       | LPAREN expression RPAREN


